Hey, hey, hey, hey!

23:48.634 --> 23:50.133
Come on!

23:50.167 --> 23:52.334
It's quittin' time.
Let's go home.

23:52.367 --> 23:53.601
Take it easy, huh?

23:53.634 --> 23:54.634
Okay, bye-bye.

